{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>TL;DR:</u></strong> <i>Be the villain! This game will tickle that <u>action-magic-fantasy-nerve</u>, and if you are looking for hours of entertainment: <u>give this game a try</u>! (There is a free demo!)</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>A fast-paced, yet tactical, action-roguelite!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/CraigaKnocksDwarves1.gif?t=1737703165\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Turn the Empire against itself!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/Cain_sowing_chaos.gif?t=1737703165\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Create powerful synergies and combos from the chaos you created!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/Graethal_corpse_explosionEPIC-shorter.gif?t=1737703165\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Customize your playstyle:</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/Show_attack_settings.gif?t=1737703165\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Fight off evil enemies and demonic creatures!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2975180/extras/Blizzie-IceFairyFight.gif?t=1737703165\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><u>Detailed features:</u></strong> (so far, as more will be added)</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>6 playable characters</strong>, each very different from the next. Each has six unique spells, six unique passive skills, and there are 12 base skills anyone can choose from.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Terrain matters</strong>: Fires spread rapidly on grass, water can be frozen, pits can be fallen into.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Wild skill combinations</strong>, allowing for completely unique playthroughs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Unique items with randomized qualities</strong>, exponentially adding combos and variety to the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>35 Steam Achievements</strong>, rewarding players when starting new games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Each playthrough is a mini-campaign</strong>, starting at a small village and ending in the halls of the emperor's castle. The path will vary, taking you through magical glades, towns, fortresses, or dwarven mines.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>7 different bosses.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dozens of enemies</strong>, each with variable stats and traits.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hand-pixeled coziness</strong>, details, and indie warmth!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A unique and adventurous <strong>original soundtrack.</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Hours of fun at a cheap price!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All of these features will be expanded upon: more characters, spells, item abilities, areas, enemies, bosses, the soundtrack, etc. There will also be new playmodes! Stay tuned!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"A new god!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2975180/76debaebc9f6cc7b7fdee85e01f85a6700ecd775.jpg"},{"name":"It really did burn!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/publi